| stale data test          | WebSocket更新停止時のhalt条件                                    |
| reconciliation test      | local position と exchange position の差分                   |
| parity test              | baseline vs NautilusTrader                               |
| Hummingbot adapter smoke | config生成、runtime path分離、no secrets                       |
| HftBacktest smoke        | L2 synthetic order book replay                           |

