# 10. Strategy promotion pipeline

```text
idea
→ fast screen
→ research backtest
→ baseline deterministic check
→ Nautilus event-driven backtest
→ paper trading
→ limited live
→ scaled live
→ retired / paused
```

| Stage                 | Input                                 | Output                       | Gate                                    | Failure時         |
| --------------------- | ------------------------------------- | ---------------------------- | --------------------------------------- | ---------------- |
| idea                  | hypothesis, venue, pair, product type | StrategySpec draft           | product type / data / venueが明確          | park             |
| fast screen           | OHLCV/factor data                     | CandidateReport              | trade count, rough edge, fee耐性          | reject           |
| research backtest     | walk-forward/OOS                      | ResearchReport               | OOS stability, parameter stability      | revise           |
| baseline check        | SignalFrame                           | expected orders/fills/equity | no-lookahead, accounting, fee/funding   | block            |
| event-driven backtest | Nautilus catalog                      | EventBacktestReport          | order lifecycle, slippage, partial fill | revise execution |
| paper trading         | live/paper venue                      | PaperLedger                  | signal parity, order reconciliation     | pause            |
| limited live          | small capital                         | LiveLedger                   | max loss, stale data, position limit    | halt             |
| scaled live           | approved capital                      | ProductionLedger             | net PnL, capacity, drawdown             | reduce/retire    |

## live昇格条件

```text
unit/schema/golden tests pass
crypto fee/funding tests pass
baseline deterministic check pass
baseline vs Nautilus parity pass
Nautilus historical event backtest pass
paper signal parity pass
paper order reconciliation pass
stale data halt test pass
kill switch test pass
max daily loss test pass
position limit test pass
manual approval
```

## live停止条件

```text
max daily loss breach
max drawdown breach
exchange position mismatch
wallet/balance mismatch
stale market data
unexpected order state
unexpected partial fill behavior
funding/cost drift
latency threshold breach
API error storm
exchange maintenance/outage
manual kill switch
```

